TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select account_id, cast((has_postpaid + case bundle when '1P' then 1 when '2P' then 2 when '3P' then 3 else 0 end) as varchar(2))||'P' as u_PROD_CONVERGENCE_GROUP from ( sel account_id, max(case when subs_prd_type_group = 'Mobile Postpaid' then 1 else 0 end) as has_postpaid, max(case when bundle_group='others' then null else bundle_group end) as bundle from ( sel distinct s.account_id, b.subs_prd_type_group, bundle_group from vdw_subscription s inner join vdw_rate_package rp on s.rate_package_id = rp.rate_package_id inner join vdw_product p on rp.rate_plan_product_id = p.product_id inner join vdn_product_grouping_bi b on p.product_id = b.product_id where s.subscription_status_id = 1 and b.subs_prd_type_group in ('Mobile Postpaid' ,'WIN') ) a group by 1 ) b

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT fmh.Account_Id , fmh.Migration_Status AS MIGRATION_STATUS , fmh.Migration_Scenario AS MIGRATION_SCENARIO , CASE /*Based on Definition from Marketing*/ WHEN LOWER(fmh.Premium_Channel) like 'premium plus%' AND ((fmh.Source_Product like '%+%' OR LOWER(fmh.Source_Product) like 'sunrise home unlimited%') OR sub.Win_TV_Component IS NULL) THEN 'price increase w/premium 10' /*1st in case order*/
WHEN (LOWER(fmh.Premium_Channel) not like 'premium plus%' OR fmh.Premium_Channel IS NULL) AND ((fmh.Source_Product like '%+%' OR LOWER(fmh.Source_Product) like 'sunrise home unlimited%') OR ((LOWER(fmh.Target_TV_Rate_Plan) like '%tv hzn%' OR LOWER(fmh.Target_TV_Rate_Plan) like '%tv (hzn)%') AND (LOWER(sub.Rate_Package_Name) like '%tv hzn%' OR LOWER(sub.Rate_Package_Name) like '%tv (hzn)%')))THEN 'price neutral' /*2nd in case order*/
WHEN LOWER(sub.Win_TV_Component) IN ('tv start','we tv m','we tv (m)') THEN 'price increase' /*3rd in case order*/
WHEN LOWER(fmh.Premium_Channel) like 'premium plus%' AND LOWER(sub.Win_TV_Component) IN ('we tv l','tv comfort','we tv (l)') THEN 'price increase with premium' /*4th in case order*/
WHEN LOWER(sub.Win_TV_Component) IN ('we tv l','tv comfort','we tv (l)') THEN 'price decrease' /*5th in case order*/ /*a new WHEN possible to fill the blanks when Premium_Channel is present: Marketing to confirm (mail on 02.06.2022 to Valentina Concepito)*/ ELSE NULL /*here we pottentially might say ELSE 'price neutral' */ END AS MIGRATION_PRICE_IMPACT
FROM vdw_Fixnet_Mass_Migration_Hist fmh LEFT JOIN (SELECT s.account_id, s.subscription_id, rp.rate_package_name, b.Win_TV_Component FROM vdw_Fixnet_Mass_Migration_Hist fmh JOIN vdw_subscription s on fmh.subscription_id = s.subscription_id and fmh.Pre_Migration_Date>= s.Activation_dttm INNER JOIN vdw_rate_package rp ON s.rate_package_id = rp.rate_package_id INNER JOIN vdw_product p on rp.rate_plan_product_id = p.product_id LEFT JOIN vdw_product_grouping b ON p.product_id = b.product_id AND b.Win_TV_Component not in ('0', 'NA') WHERE fmh.end_date='9999-12-31' GROUP BY 1,2,3,4) sub ON sub.subscription_id = fmh.subscription_id WHERE fmh.end_date='9999-12-31' QUALIFY RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY fmh.Account_id ORDER BY fmh.Start_Date, fmh.Execution_Date DESC)=1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: /*YAL_LEB_SWYPE or regular Sunrise surveys*/ select coalesce(Source_Key_2,'')||external_Account_Number ||'-'||trim(cast(survey_id as varchar(30)))||'-'||cast(cast(transaction_date as date format'YYYYMMDD') as varchar(8)) survey_record_id, s.interaction_id, s.account_id, s.event_id, s.subscription_id, s.order_id, s.survey_id, s.brand_id from (sel * from vdw_survey_input where survey_id not in (31,16,18))s left join vdw_Accounts a on a.Account_Id= s.Account_Id left join (select * from vct_rt_Brand where source_table_name = 'LEBARA_SALES_DATA_SIM' or Source_Key_2 = 'SWYPE')b on s.brand_Id = b.brand_id group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8 union select external_Account_Number ||'-'||trim(cast(survey_id as varchar(30)))||'-'||cast(cast(transaction_date as date format'YYYYMMDD') as varchar(8)) survey_record_id, s.interaction_id, s.account_id, s.event_id, s.subscription_id, s.order_id, s.survey_id, s.brand_id from (sel * from vdw_survey_input where survey_id in (31))s left join vdw_Accounts a on a.Account_Id= s.Account_Id left join (select * from vct_rt_Brand where source_table_name = 'LEBARA_SALES_DATA_SIM')b on s.brand_Id = b.brand_id group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8 union /*BC Sunrise*/ select coalesce(Source_Key_2,'')||external_Account_Number ||'_'||trim(cast(survey_id as varchar(30)))||'_'||coalesce(Interaction_Cd,Contact_Event_Cd )||'_' ||cast(cast(transaction_date as date format'YYYYMMDD') as varchar(8)) survey_record_id, s.interaction_id, s.account_id, s.event_id, s.subscription_id, s.order_id, s.survey_id, 1 AS brand_id from (sel * from vdw_survey_input where survey_Id in (16,18))s left join vdw_Accounts a on a.Account_Id= s.Account_Id left join vdw_Interaction i on s.interaction_id = i.interaction_Id left join vdw_contact_event c on c.Event_ID= s.Event_id left join (select * from vct_rt_Brand where source_table_name = 'LEBARA_SALES_DATA_SIM')b on s.brand_Id = b.brand_id where s.brand_id <> 17 group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8 union /*BC UPC*/ sel trim(Account_Id)||'_'||trim(cast(survey_id as varchar(30)))||'_'||trim(case when Interaction_Id = 0 then Event_Id else Interaction_id end )||'_' ||cast(cast(transaction_date as date format'YYYYMMDD') as varchar(8)) survey_record_id, s.interaction_id, s.account_id, s.event_id, s.subscription_id, s.order_id, s.survey_id, s.brand_id from (sel * from vdw_survey_input where survey_Id in (16,18) and brand_id = 17 )s group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT COALESCE(A.Account_Id, M.Account_Id, EF.Account_Id) as Account_Id, A.ACCO_NUMBER_SUBSCRIBERS, COALESCE(M.New_Segment, EF.New_Segment) AS New_Segment FROM ( select ash.account_Id, count(distinct Subscription_Id) as ACCO_NUMBER_SUBSCRIBERS from vdw_account_subscription_hist ash where end_date = date'9999-12-31' group by 1 ) A FULL JOIN ( SELECT a.account_id, 'Medinex' AS New_Segment FROM vdw_accounts a INNER JOIN vdw_account_sub_type_hist asth ON a.account_id = asth.account_id AND asth.end_date = date'9999-12-31' INNER JOIN vdw_account_sub_type ast ON ast.account_sub_type_id = asth.account_sub_type_id INNER JOIN vdw_account_sub_type_category cat ON cat.account_sub_type_category_id=ast.account_sub_type_category_id WHERE cat.Account_Sub_Type_Cat_Name in ('MEDI1', 'MEDI2') GROUP BY 1,2 ) M ON A.Account_Id = M.Account_Id FULL JOIN ( SELECT aah.Account_Id, CASE aah.Attribute_Value WHEN 'Employee of the Firm' THEN 'EOF' WHEN 'Friends of the Firm' THEN 'FOF' ELSE NULL END As New_Segment FROM vdw_Account_Attribute_Hist aah WHERE aah.Attribute_Value IN ('Employee of the Firm','Friends of the Firm') AND aah.End_Date = DATE'9999-12-31' GROUP BY 1,2 ) EF ON A.Account_Id = EF.Account_Id

INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Partner_Group_Hist l ON sph.Sales_Partner_Party_Id = l.Sales_Partner_Party_Id AND l.Source_Id = 9 AND l.End_Date = 80991231
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Channel_Level sg_l ON l.Sales_Group_Id = sg_l.Sales_Group_Id
WHERE sph.End_Date = 80991231 AND sph.Source_Id = 9 AND sph.Sales_Creating_Group_Id = 16 AND sg_l.Sales_Group_Name = 'YOL Online'
union SELECT DISTINCT sph.Sap_Sales_Code, 'Buy' sc, 'Online' types FROM vdw_Sales_Partner_Hist sph
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Partner_Group_Hist l ON sph.Sales_Partner_Party_Id = l.Sales_Partner_Party_Id AND l.Source_Id = 9 AND l.End_Date = 80991231
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Channel_Level sg_l ON l.Sales_Group_Id = sg_l.Sales_Group_Id
WHERE sph.End_Date = 80991231 AND sph.Source_Id = 9 AND sph.Sales_Creating_Group_Id = 16 AND sg_l.Sales_Group_Name = 'YOL Online'
union SELECT DISTINCT sph.Sap_Sales_Code, 'Fixline and Internet' sc, 'Online' types FROM vdw_Sales_Partner_Hist sph
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Partner_Group_Hist l ON sph.Sales_Partner_Party_Id = l.Sales_Partner_Party_Id AND l.Source_Id = 9 AND l.End_Date = 80991231
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Channel_Level sg_l ON l.Sales_Group_Id = sg_l.Sales_Group_Id
WHERE sph.End_Date = 80991231 AND sph.Source_Id = 9 AND sph.Sales_Creating_Group_Id = 16 AND sg_l.Sales_Group_Name = 'YOL Online'
union SELECT DISTINCT sph.Sap_Sales_Code, 'Mobile Prepaid' sc, 'Online' types FROM vdw_Sales_Partner_Hist sph
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Partner_Group_Hist l ON sph.Sales_Partner_Party_Id = l.Sales_Partner_Party_Id AND l.Source_Id = 9 AND l.End_Date = 80991231
INNER JOIN vdw_Sales_Channel_Level sg_l ON l.Sales_Group_Id = sg_l.Sales_Group_Id
WHERE sph.End_Date = 80991231 AND sph.Source_Id = 9 AND sph.Sales_Creating_Group_Id = 16 AND sg_l.Sales_Group_Name = 'YOL Online' ) aa

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: sel s.subscription_id, p.product_name||'-'||trim(rp.device_duration) as prod_device_plan, case when product_group = 'Home 5G' then product_group when subs_prd_type_group = 'WIN' then case when tv_indicator = 'TV' then tv_indicator when internet_indicator = 'Internet' then 'Landline & Internet' else 'Fixline' end else subs_prd_type_group end as product_group, product_value, TV_NEO_DEVICES, tech.Technology_Name from vdw_subscription s inner join vdw_rate_package rp on s.rate_package_id = rp.rate_package_id inner join vdw_product p on rp.rate_plan_product_id = p.product_id left join vdn_product_grouping_bi bi on rp.rate_plan_product_id = bi.product_id LEFT JOIN ( SELECT s.Subscription_Id , att.Attribute_Value as TV_NEO_DEVICES FROM vdw_Subscription s INNER JOIN vdw_Subscription_Product_Attr_ att ON s.Subscription_Id = att.Subscription_Id AND s.Subscription_Status_Id = 1 INNER JOIN vct_rt_product_attribute pa ON att.Product_Attribute_Id = pa.Product_Attribute_Id WHERE pa.Product_Attribute_Name = 'TV Neo Devices' AND att.End_Date = DATE'9999-12-31' QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY s.Subscription_Id ORDER BY att.Start_Date DESC) = 1 ) tv ON s.Subscription_Id = tv.Subscription_Id LEFT JOIN ( SELECT sph.Subscription_Id, p.Product_Name as Technology_Name FROM vDW_Subscription_Product_Hist sph INNER JOIN vDW_Product p ON sph.Product_Id = p.Product_Id AND p.Product_Type_Id IN ( SELECT CAST(TRIM(Condition_Value) AS INTEGER) FROM vCT_Nps_Etl_Condition_Control WHERE Attribute_Name='NPS_CUST_BASE_TECHNOLOGY_INCL' ) AND sph.End_Date='9999-12-31' QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY sph.Subscription_Id ORDER BY Deactivation_Dttm DESC, Activation_Dttm DESC)=1 ) tech ON s.Subscription_Id = tech.Subscription_Id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: sel x.account_id, count(*) as n_SITE_NUMBER_INTERACTIONS from( select i.account_id , i.interaction_id , case when i.Interaction_Origin_Id = 41 or i.Origin_System = 'VIA' then 'No' when i.Interaction_Automatic_Flag = 1 or (i.Inserted_By in ('sa', 'API/Cbbatch/Chewbacca', 'Cbbatch/Chewbacca', 'Cbbatch','crm_api_user') and i.System_User_Id = 142274) or (i.Source_Id = 89 and i.Inserted_By is null) then 'Yes' else 'No' end as interaction_is_automatic /*Logic received from Andrei Bantos to exclude automatic interactions*/ from vdw_interaction i inner join vdw_interaction_type it on i.interaction_type_id = it.interaction_type_id where lower(it.interaction_type_name) in ('call','visit') and cast(i.create_dttm as date) >= current_date - 180 and interaction_is_automatic = 'No' ) x group by 1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT a.Account_Id , a.Activation_Dttm , a.n_ACCO_SUBS_START_DATE , a.n_ACCO_SUBS_EXPIRY_DATE , neo.TV_NEO_DEVICES_Acc , COALESCE(tech.Technology_Name, upctech.Technology) as Technology_Name_Acc FROM ( select a.account_id, a.activation_dttm, min(ch.contract_start_dttm) as n_ACCO_SUBS_START_DATE, max(ch.expire_dttm) as n_ACCO_SUBS_EXPIRY_DATE from vdw_accounts a left join vdw_account_contract_hist ach on a.account_id= ach.account_id left join vdw_contract_hist ch on ch.contract_id = ach.contract_id group by 1,2 ) a LEFT JOIN ( SELECT s.Account_Id , s.Subscription_Id , att.Attribute_Value as TV_NEO_DEVICES_Acc FROM vdw_Subscription s INNER JOIN vdw_Subscription_Product_Attr_ att ON s.Subscription_Id = att.Subscription_Id AND s.Subscription_Status_Id = 1 INNER JOIN vct_rt_product_attribute pa ON att.Product_Attribute_Id = pa.Product_Attribute_Id WHERE pa.Product_Attribute_Name = 'TV Neo Devices' AND att.End_Date = DATE'9999-12-31' QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY s.Account_Id ORDER BY CHARACTER_LENGTH(att.Attribute_Value) DESC) = 1 ) neo ON a.Account_Id = neo.Account_Id LEFT JOIN ( SELECT s.Account_Id, p.Product_Name as Technology_Name FROM vDW_Subscription_Product_Hist sph INNER JOIN vdw_Subscription s ON sph.Subscription_Id = s.Subscription_Id INNER JOIN vDW_Product p ON sph.Product_Id = p.Product_Id AND p.Product_Type_Id IN ( SELECT CAST(TRIM(Condition_Value) AS INTEGER) FROM vCT_Nps_Etl_Condition_Control WHERE Attribute_Name='NPS_CUST_BASE_TECHNOLOGY_INCL' ) AND sph.End_Date='9999-12-31' QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY s.Account_Id ORDER BY sph.Deactivation_Dttm DESC, sph.Activation_Dttm DESC)=1 ) tech ON a.Account_Id = tech.Account_Id LEFT JOIN /*UPC Technology*/ ( SELECT aah.account_id, hfc.access_technology as Technology FROM vdw_account_address_hist aah INNER JOIN vdw_postal_address pa ON pa.address_id=aah.address_id INNER JOIN UPC_CR_FLAT_HFC hfc ON CAST(pa.additional_address_line AS INTEGER)= hfc.location_flat_id WHERE aah.source_id=89 AND aah.address_usage_id=5 /*primary address*/ AND aah.address_type_id=1 AND aah.end_date=CAST('9999-12-31' AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND hfc.access_technology IS NOT NULL QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY aah.Account_Id ORDER BY hfc.access_technology DESC) = 1 /*HFC most prior*/ ) upctech ON a.Account_id = upctech.Account_Id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT sp.Sap_Sales_Code AS UNIT_SHOP_ID_LKP , CASE WHEN u.sap_sales_code is not null THEN 'Sunrise Centers' ELSE sr.retail_channel END AS SURVEY_RETAIL_CHANNEL_LDR
FROM vdw_sales_partner_hist sp
LEFT JOIN vdw_sales_partner_hist p on sp.sales_partner_party_id=p.sales_partner_party_id and p.end_date=cast('9999-12-31' as date format 'yyyy-mm-dd') and p.source_id=9
LEFT JOIN vDW_Survey_Agent_Org_Hier_Hist osh on p.sap_sales_code=osh.agent_cd and osh.end_date='9999-12-31' and lower(osh.Org_Group) in (select trim(lower(condition_value)) from vCT_Etl_Condition_Control where attribute_name='NPS_SHOP_RTL_GROUP_INCL')
LEFT OUTER JOIN Medallia_Retail_Channel sr on osh.org_group=sr.Org_Group
LEFT JOIN vDW_Survey_Agent_Org_Hier_Hist osh2 on sp.sap_sales_code=osh2.agent_cd and osh2.end_date='9999-12-31' and lower(osh2.team_level_1) not in (select trim(lower(condition_value)) from vCT_Etl_Condition_Control where attribute_name='NPS_SHOP_TL1_EXCL') LEFT JOIN vdw_system_user u on u.sap_sales_code=osh2.agent_cd AND lower(u.work_group) in (select trim(lower(condition_value)) from vCT_Etl_Condition_Control where attribute_name='NPS_SHOP_AGN_CLF_WRK_GRP')
WHERE sp.end_date=cast('9999-12-31' as date format 'yyyy-mm-dd') AND sp.source_id=9 AND SURVEY_RETAIL_CHANNEL_LDR IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1,2

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select distinct a.account_Id from vdw_orders o -- information about an account inner join vdw_Order_Account_Hist H on O.order_id=H.order_id and H.end_date='9999-12-31' inner join vdw_accounts a on H.Account_id = a.account_id and a.source_id = 2 -- information about status inner join vdw_Order_Status_Hist T on O.order_id=T.order_id and T.end_date='9999-12-31' -- decode status id to name inner join vdw_Order_Status G on T.order_status_id=G.order_status_id -- find product related to order inner join vdw_Order_Product_Hist OH on o.Order_Id = OH.Order_Id and oh.end_date='9999-12-31' inner join vdw_Product_Related_Hist R on OH.product_id=R.product_id and R.end_date= '9999-12-31' -- add product grouping inner join Vdn_Product_Grouping_Bi B on R.Related_Product_Id=B.product_id -- get last provisioning step inner join vdw_order_provisioning_hist oph on o.order_id = oph.order_id and oph.end_date = '9999-12-31' -- apply condition filters where brand_id = 1 /* 'Sunrise' */ and O.order_type_id in (2,6) /* Conversion, New */ and b.product_group in ( select trim(condition_value) from vct_etl_condition_control where attribute_name='NPS_ACT_WINTV_PRD_GRP_INCL' ) -- determine 'open' orders and G.Order_Status_Name in (select condition_value FROM vct_NPS_ETL_CONDITION_CONTROL WHERE TRIM(control_id) = '326' and attribute_name ='NPS_TCHPT_EXCL_ORD_STAT_EXP_FF') and oph.order_provisioning_step_id in (921) /* Wait for Activation */
